    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>During execution of <b>feature/UniversalEnrollmentPositiveOhio.feature</b> for OHD plans, while validating the test case <em>“Enrollment of Individual Account with KIS and ABI One-Time Bank Contribution Option and Beneficiary DOB Edit”</em>, an issue is observed on the <b>Account Identification (ID Verification) page</b>.</p>

<p>The <b>“Military I.D. Card”</b> option is <b>not displayed in the ID Card Type dropdown</b>, although it exists in the Test CSV Data.</p>

<hr />

<h3><a name="Environment%3A"></a><b>Environment:</b></h3>

<ul>
	<li>Stage1</li>
	<li>Ohio 529 Enrollment application</li>
	<li>URL: Enrollment → Account Identification page</li>
</ul>


<hr />

<h3><a name="StepstoReproduce%3A"></a><b>Steps to Reproduce:</b></h3>

<ol>
	<li>Navigate to Ohio 529 enrollment (Stage1)</li>
	<li>Start Individual Account enrollment flow</li>
	<li>Proceed with KIS and ABI One-Time Bank Contribution option</li>
	<li>Navigate to <b>Account Identification page</b></li>
	<li>Click on <b>ID Card Type dropdown</b></li>
	<li>Observe available options</li>
</ol>


<hr />

<h3><a name="ActualResult%3A"></a><b>Actual Result:</b></h3>

<ul>
	<li>Dropdown options displayed:
	<ul>
		<li>Driver’s License</li>
		<li>State Issued I.D. Card</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li>❌ “Military I.D. Card” option is <b>missing</b></li>
</ul>


<hr />

<h3><a name="ExpectedResult%3A"></a><b>Expected Result:</b></h3>

<ul>
	<li>✅ “Military I.D. Card” should be available in the dropdown, as it is present in CSV file:
	<ul>
		<li><tt>AO_IDENTIFICATION_TYPE</tt></li>
	</ul>
	</li>
</ul>


<hr />

<h3><a name="Evidence%3A"></a><b>Evidence:</b></h3>

<ul>
	<li>UI Screenshot: Shows only Driver’s License &amp; State Issed I.D. Card</li>
	<li>DB Screenshot: Shows multiple entries for “Military I.D. Card”</li>
</ul>


<hr />

<h3><a name="Impact%3A"></a><b>Impact:</b></h3>

<ul>
	<li>Users cannot select Military ID for identity verification</li>
	<li>Causes <b>functional gap between UI and Test Data(CSV FILE)</b></li>
	<li>May impact enrollment completion for applicable users</li>
</ul>




<p><b>Screenshot:</b><br/>
In Automation CSV</p>

